high_descs: Turn left, turn left, walk straight towards the white table
Pick up the silver knife on the table
Turn right, walk straight towards the fridge
Open the fridge, slice the fruit inside, and close the fridge
Turn right, walk straight, turn left towards the cabinet
Place the knife on top of the cabinet
Turn left, walk straight, turn right towards the fridge
Open the fridge and take out the sliced piece of fruit
Close the fridge, turn right, walk straight, turn left towards the stove
Place the fruit in the microwave above, set the timer, close the microwave, open the microwave, take out the fruit
Turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right towards the small black table
Place the fruit on top of the small black table
anns.task_desc: Place a piece of microwaved fruit on the black table

high_descs: Turn around, go to the white table.
Take the left small knife from the table.
Turn right, go to the fridge.
Cut the right potato on the lower shelf in the fridge.
Go to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Put the knife on the counter.
Go back to the fridge on the left.
Take a slice of potato from the fridge.
Turn right, go to the oven.
Put the slice of potato in the microwave above the oven. Turn on the microwave. Take the potato from the oven.
Turn around, go to the door, turn right, go to the black stand.
Put the potato on the lower right corner of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on a stand.

high_descs: Move to the white rectangular table across the room.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter next to the large carving knife.
Turn left and move across the room to the fridge.
Open the door and cut the potato that is on the shelf.  Shut the door.
Turn right and move to the small counter top next to the fridge.
Put the knife down on the counter.
Turn left and move back to the refrigerator.
Take a slice of potato out of the fridge.
Move across the room until you reach the microwave.
Place the potato inside the microwave and cook it.  Remove the cooked potato.
Move across the room to the small black table.
Place the potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Use knife to slice potato, cook potato in microwave, followed by placing on black table.
